# 🧠 CryptoBuddy: Your First AI-Powered Financial Sidekick! 🌟

Welcome to CryptoBuddy — a beginner-friendly, AI-powered chatbot that helps users choose the right cryptocurrency based on profitability and sustainability.

## 🚀 Project Overview

This chatbot uses basic AI decision-making logic to recommend cryptocurrencies from a predefined dataset. It’s built with simple `if-else` statements in Python to demonstrate how AI can make choices based on trends and criteria.

## 🔍 Features

- Responds to user queries about crypto trends
- Gives investment suggestions based on price trends and sustainability
- Offers advice using rule-based logic
- Beginner-friendly and easily expandable

## 🛠 Tools Used

- Python 3
- Google Colab / Jupyter Notebook
- Dataset: Predefined in code (no external API required)

## 🗂 Dataset

```python
crypto_db = {
    "Bitcoin": {
        "price_trend": "rising",
        "market_cap": "high",
        "energy_use": "high",
        "sustainability_score": 3/10
    },
    "Ethereum": {
        "price_trend": "stable",
        "market_cap": "high",
        "energy_use": "medium",
        "sustainability_score": 6/10
    },
    "Cardano": {
        "price_trend": "rising",
        "market_cap": "medium",
        "energy_use": "low",
        "sustainability_score": 8/10
    }
}
